  "text": "MDC1C is inherited as an autosomal recessive disorder with linkage to chromosome 19q13.3. Mutations of the FKRP gene include homozygous and heterozygous missense and nonsense mutations [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] .",
